json.description: Discover the perfect place to build your dream home on this 3.08-acre wooded lot located in the upscale gated community of Mountain Creek Hollow, nestled in the scenic foothills of the North Georgia Mountains. With paved road frontage on both the upper and lower sides and varied terrain including gentle, buildable areas, this private and peaceful lot offers both accessibility and natural charm.  Mountain Creek Hollow spans approximately 275 acres of rolling, forested land with streams, mountain views, and thoughtfully maintained amenities. Residents enjoy access to a trout pond, butterfly garden, hiking trails, and a covered bridge. A neighborhood pavilion and picnic area sit beside the rushing Fausett Creek, which runs throughout the community and includes picturesque waterfalls. Additional features include a community garden, paved walking trail, small pond, and a charming water wheel.  Ideally situated between Ellijay and Jasper, the location is convenient to local wineries, restaurants, shops, and entertainment.  Please note: Short-term rentals are not permitted in this community.

json.description: Welcome to an exceptional opportunity to own 4.7 wooded acres in the prestigious gated community of Mountain Creek Hollow, nestled in the scenic foothills of the North Georgia Mountains. This unique property combines two adjacent parcels, one 3.08 acres and the other 1.62 acres, creating an expansive homesite with endless possibilities for your dream retreat.  With paved road frontage on both the upper and lower sides, the property offers excellent accessibility and flexibility for building. The terrain features a mix of gentle, buildable areas and natural wooded privacy, giving you the perfect balance of charm and functionality. A Level 3 soil test has already been completed on one of the lots, saving you valuable time and providing peace of mind as you plan your future home.  Mountain Creek Hollow spans approximately 275 acres of rolling, forested land, thoughtfully designed to preserve its natural beauty while offering residents a wide range of amenities. Within the community, you'll find a stocked trout pond, a butterfly garden, scenic hiking trails, and a picturesque covered bridge. A charming water wheel and small pond add to the rustic mountain atmosphere, while a neighborhood pavilion and picnic area overlook rushing Fausett Creek and its waterfalls. A community garden and paved walking trail provide even more opportunities to enjoy the outdoors and connect with neighbors.  Ideally situated between Ellijay and Jasper, this location allows you to enjoy peaceful mountain living while still being close to local wineries, restaurants, shops, and entertainment. Please note that short-term rentals are not permitted in Mountain Creek Hollow, ensuring a serene and stable neighborhood atmosphere.  This is a rare opportunity to secure a combined 4.7-acre property in one of Gilmer County's most desirable gated communities, offering the perfect setting for your custom-built mountain dream home.

json.description: Escape to the North Georgia mountains and experience the perfect blend of privacy, beauty, and convenience. This 3.18-acre wooded property offers the rare freedom of no HOA and no restrictions, giving you endless possibilities-whether you're dreaming of a custom mountain home, a cozy cabin getaway, or a profitable short-term rental.    Surrounded by towering hardwoods and rolling terrain, this property provides a serene backdrop for morning coffee on your future porch, evenings under star-filled skies, and weekends filled with outdoor adventures.    Just a short drive away, you'll find downtown Ellijay, known for its charming shops, wineries, and famous apple orchards. Outdoor enthusiasts will love the proximity to hiking trails, rivers, and fishing spots-making this location ideal for both relaxation and recreation.    Enjoy the peace and seclusion of the mountains without sacrificing modern conveniences. Whether you're seeking a second home, investment opportunity, or full-time residence, this property offers a chance to create your own North Georgia retreat.

json.description: Discover your own private mountain escape on this stunning **6.87-acre lot** located in a gated community in beautiful **Ellijay, GA**. Perched high above the valley, this property offers **breathtaking panoramic views of the Blue Ridge Mountains** and the rare opportunity to own land **adjacent to the Chattahoochee National Forest**.  With nearly 7 acres of pristine, wooded land, this homesite combines seclusion, security, and unmatched natural beauty-perfect for building your dream mountain retreat or vacation getaway. Enjoy the serenity of mountain living while being just a short drive to historic downtown Ellijay, renowned for its apple orchards, wineries, hiking trails, and outdoor recreation.  Whether you're looking for a peaceful full-time residence or a weekend getaway, this property provides the perfect backdrop for endless mountain views and a true connection with nature.  Come experience the beauty and tranquility of North Georgia living-this is the mountain property you've been waiting for!
